</a><div class="tile-outline" aria-hidden="true"></div></article></div></div></div></section><section class="wp-block-cbr-flks-one-column alignfull cbr-flks-one-column simple-columns pt-30 pb-30"><div class="container-fluid container-fluid-wrapper"><div class="row"><div class="d-flex justify-content-between flex-wrap has-1-column"><div class="col-12"><div class="wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-16018d1d wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex"><div class="wp-block-button is-style-fill"><a class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://cyberfolks.pl/blog/">więcej wiedzy na blogu</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="wp-block-cbr-flks-one-column alignfull cbr-flks-one-column simple-columns pt-50 pb-80 cf-pattern-featured-in"><div class="container-fluid container-fluid-wrapper"><div class="row"><div class="d-flex justify-content-between flex-wrap has-1-column"><div class="col-12"><h2 class="wp-block-heading is-style-header-gt">Piszą o nas</h2><div class="wp-block-columns pt-80 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex"><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow"><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="alignright size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="40" height="38" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quotation_mark_icon.png" alt="" class="wp-image-38660"/></figure></div><div class="wp-block-group cf-pattern-featured-in__content"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p>Nie&nbsp;martw się, nie&nbsp;musisz być programistą, żeby&nbsp;przyspieszyć działanie Twojej&nbsp;strony. Wystarczy, że&nbsp;wybierzesz hosting, który&nbsp;będzie miał odpowiednie narzędzia (…) Cyber_Boost to&nbsp;pakiet, który&nbsp;zbiera wszystkie te technologiczne rozwiązania w&nbsp;jednym (…).</p></div></div><figure class="wp-block-image size-medium is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="300" height="108" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/grafmag-logo-black-300x108.png" alt="" class="wp-image-25275" style="width:150px;height:54px" srcset="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/grafmag-logo-black-300x108.png 300w, https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/grafmag-logo-black-1024x367.png 1024w, https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/grafmag-logo-black-768x275.png 768w, https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/grafmag-logo-black.png 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></figure></div><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow"><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="alignright size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="40" height="38" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quotation_mark_icon.png" alt="" class="wp-image-38660"/></figure></div><div class="wp-block-group cf-pattern-featured-in__content"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p>Musisz pamiętać o tym, że firmy hostingowe nie trzymają kopii zapasowych w nieskończoność. To byłoby zbyt kosztowne. Przyjęło się, że przechowują dane z ostatnich dwóch dni, jednak to w mojej opinii zdecydowanie za krótko. Im dłużej przechowywane są dane (np. w hostingu cyber_Folks jest to 28 dni wstecz), tym większa szansa na to, że będzie można z nich skorzystać, kiedy faktycznie zauważymy problem.</p></div></div><figure class="wp-block-image size-medium is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="300" height="67" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/spidersweb_logo-300x67.png" alt="" class="wp-image-25271" style="width:150px;height:34px" srcset="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/spidersweb_logo-300x67.png 300w, https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/spidersweb_logo.png 476w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></figure></div><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow"><div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="alignright size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="40" height="38" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quotation_mark_icon.png" alt="" class="wp-image-38660"/></figure></div><div class="wp-block-group cf-pattern-featured-in__content"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"><p>Bezpieczeństwo i ochrona marki to kolejne narzędzie na cyber_Folks, które pozwoli sprawdzić czy wybrana przez klienta domena może być wykorzystana do różnych form ataków, takich jak typosquatting, cybersquatting czy atak homograficzny. To pozwoli już na etapie doboru domeny wybrać dla klienta taką, która jest najmniej podatna na takie ataki.</p></div></div><figure class="wp-block-image size-medium is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="300" height="49" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/antyweb_logo_poziom_czarne-300x49.png" alt="" class="wp-image-31955" style="width:150px;height:25px" srcset="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/antyweb_logo_poziom_czarne-300x49.png 300w, https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/antyweb_logo_poziom_czarne-1024x168.png 1024w, https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/antyweb_logo_poziom_czarne-768x126.png 768w, https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/antyweb_logo_poziom_czarne-1536x253.png 1536w, https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/antyweb_logo_poziom_czarne-2048x337.png 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></figure></div></div><div style="height:188px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading is-style-header-gt pb-80">Zaufało nam ponad 350 000 klientów</h2><figure class="wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-5 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex"><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="271" height="140" data-id="52838" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/mennicapolska-271x140-1.png" alt="" class="wp-image-52838"/></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="271" height="140" data-id="52905" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/itaka-271x140-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-52905"/></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="271" height="140" data-id="53328" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/logo-blik.png" alt="" class="wp-image-53328"/></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="271" height="140" data-id="52901" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/luxmed-271x140-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-52901"/></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="271" height="140" data-id="52023" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/click-meeting-271x140-1.png" alt="" class="wp-image-52023"/></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="271" height="140" data-id="52912" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/budmat.png" alt="" class="wp-image-52912"/></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="271" height="140" data-id="52924" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/danone.png" alt="" class="wp-image-52924"/></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="271" height="140" data-id="52918" src="https://cyberfolks.pl/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/tymbark.png" alt="" class="wp-image-52918"/></figure><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="271" height="